https://www.marmiton.org/recettes/recette_gratin-de-courgettes-rapide_17071.aspx

3 courgettes (1KG)

cook in pan one by one
for each :
    2 olive oil
    salt, pepper
    (position first high)
25g beurre demi sel
2 bouchons olive oil

100g gruyere rapé to put on top

100g grueyere rapé to mix in
25g parmesan
2 eggs
15cl creme fraiche
salt and pepper to taste

180C 30 minutes


